| Toys | 0.62 | 0.62 | 0.62 | 8 |
| Tricks and Pranks | 0.50 | 0.38 | 0.43 | 8 |
| Woodworking | 0.50 | 0.50 | 0.50 | 8 |
| Accuracy |  |  | 0.55 | 40 |
| Macro Avg | 0.56 | 0.55 | 0.54 | 40 |
| Weighted Avg | 0.56 | 0.55 | 0.54 | 40 |

